}}[[Classes]]: <u>ZChainEndSpike</u><br>
A spiked ball hanging on a chain, like a morning star flail. It can be combined with [[Classes:ZChainBit32|ZChainBit32]] and [[Classes:ZChainBit64|ZChainBit64]] to form long hanging chains by carefully adjusting the height value of each in the map editor.
